commit_message: added variation in phred scores and extended extra chunk concatenated onto end of assembly
fixed insert length so reads dont overlap
read length as param, for easier parallelizing
switched 2nd read to be the complement of the associated strand in the fasta input
fixed newlines. Python was inserting CRLF instead of LF. *sigh*
removed random assignment of paired reads, so forward reads always go in file1 and backward reads in file2
proper distributions in the db. some code tweaks
paramaterized. multiple reps and coverages. initial version of randomized distributions
initial script to split 1 fasta into 2 fastq with coverage=100
